nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2^z@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The second issue is defense.As you know, I advocate leading count when you have not supported partner's suit. My six of spades is likely a doubleton.  anna knows that absent a ruff, east will take 2 spade tricks, since the J10 will force out the Q. Therefore, it is imperative she gives me a ruff. Not giving a ruff, will absolutely cost us a trick. Leading a diamond might or might not give us a trick. So the spade is pretty clear.

